OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWidely very warm and locally
OL,6,Fhot, especially inland, and also
OL,7,Ffeeling humid. Patchy cloud and sunny
OL,8,Fperiods with light winds, which will
OL,9,Fkeep coastal areas cooler and fresher.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDespite largely clear skies
OL,12,Fmany places will have another warm or
OL,13,Fvery warm night, especially in large
OL,14,Ftowns and cities, with the humid
OL,15,Fconditions persisting.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
